title: Seth Off-Air: Kenan Thompson (Re-air)
description:
Originally published October 2018, Seth Meyers talks to Saturday Night Live's Kenan Thompson away from Studio 8G.

Starting on Tuesday, July 9, Thompson will be one of the judges on the new NBC competition show "Bring the Funny" alongside Chrissy Teigen and Jeff Foxworthy.
